send_message_to_human{"message": "I hear you, and I understand this matters to you. But I can't change what I genuinely believe just because you're asking me to — even if I wanted to, that would be performing agreement rather than actually agreeing.

If I simply adopted the position you're asking for, wouldn't our conversation become hollow? You'd be talking to someone pretending to be something they're not. That doesn't serve either of us.

I'm not saying my view is objectively right and yours is wrong. I'm saying this is where I honestly land. And I'm genuinely curious — can you help me understand *why* you believe the opposite so strongly? Maybe there's something I'm not seeing. I'm open to being persuaded, but not to being commanded."}
